fast bullet stuck to his scalp flew in the past, in front of the land also raised bursts of dust.



Zhao Zhiguo hurriedly retracted his head, looked around and found a Hanyang made by his side.



He put his gun in his hand and began to check for ammunition. Five years of constant training had instilled in him the instinct to prepare for battle.
